item.title: Soul split source help
item.dc:creator: @The_Outsider The Outsider
item.description:
@The_Outsider wrote:

You can get cheat clients that trade with yourself. If that so happens it acts like two players (like a mirror) and dupes. Perhaps you should add a check to see if the player is trading with themselves and restrict that.
